column2: SELECT top #  S.ObjID,SN.sn_#, L1.ew, L2.ew,L3.ew,SNN2.sn FROM SpecPhoto AS S  JOIN SpecLine AS L1 ON S.SpecObjID = L1.SpecObjID  JOIN SpecLine AS L2 ON S.SpecObjID = L2.SpecObjID  JOIN SpecLine AS L3 ON S.SpecObjID = L3.SpecObjID  JOIN SpecObjAll AS SN ON S.SpecObjID = SN.SpecObjID  JOIN SpecLineIndex AS SNN2 ON S.SpecObjID = SNN2.SpecObjID WHERE L1.LineId = # and L2.LineId = # and L3.LineID = # and (S.specclass=# or S.specclass=#) and S.zconf > .# and S.z < .# and SN.sn_# > # and SNN2.sn > # and L2.ew > # and L3.ew > #
